options.content:
# Shapes 

This dashboard shows different shapes with different DOM hierarchies.

Not all shapes will be drivable but this dashboard exists to show the ones
that are.

options.panelConfig:
---

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML Aliases to simplify maintenance

anchorLinks:
  - link: &threshold_db
    - {color: "semi-dark-green", level: 0}
    - {color: "orange", level: 400}
    - {color: "red", level: 800}

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Panel Config

cellIdPreamble: "cell-"
gradientMode: "hue"

cells: 
  dp0:
    dataRef: "test-data-large-cos"
    label:
      separator: "cr"
      units: "ops"
    fillColor:
      thresholds: *threshold_db
  id2:
    dataRef: "test-data-large-cos"
    label:
      separator: "cr"
      units: "ops"
    fillColor:
      thresholds: *threshold_db

panels.title: Basic draw.io rectangles with a single text type DOM leaf

options.panelConfig:
---
#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# YAML Aliases to simplify maintenance

anchorLinks:
  - link: &grafana-home
      url: "https://grafana.com/"
      params: "time"
  - link: &threshold_label
    - {color: "semi-dark-green", level: 0}
    - {color: "orange", level: 400}
    - {color: "red", level: 800}
  - link: &threshold_fill
    - {color: "orange", level: 0}
    - {color: "red", level: 400}
    - {color: "semi-dark-green", level: 800}

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Panel Config

cellIdPreamble: "cell-"
gradientMode: "hue"

cells:
  Rectangle:
    dataRef: "test-data-large-cos"
    label:
      separator: "cr"
      units: "celsius"
      decimalPoints: 1
    labelColor:
      thresholds: *threshold_label
    fillColor:
      thresholds: *threshold_fill
  Double Rectangle:
    dataRef: "test-data-large-cos"
    label:
      separator: "cr"
      units: "celsius"

  Square:

panels.title: Single and double edged shapes where the single edge shapes have the shape as a leaf

options.panelConfig:
---

#------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# Panel Config

cellIdPreamble: "cell-"
gradientMode: "hue"

cells:
  Rectangle:
    dataRef: "test-data-large-cos"
    label:
      separator: "replace"
      units: "celsius"
      decimalPoints: 1
    labelColor:
      thresholds:
        - { color: "blue", level: 0 }
        - { color: "orange", level: 400 }
        - { color: "red", level: 800 }
